lead_paragraph: Sport's highest tribunal has rejected FIFA presidential candidate Jerome Champagne's urgent request for transparent voting booths and independent scrutineers at Friday's election for the head of the global soccer body.

headline.print_headline: Sports Tribunal CAS Rejects Champagne's FIFA Voting Booth Request
